üí†Ô∏èjava.time.localDate - new Date in java 1.8
=====================

LocalDate d = LocalDate.now(); //today's date
System.out.println(d);
LocalDate d1 = LocalDate.of(2020, 8, 20);
System.out.println(d1);
LocalDate d2 = LocalDate.of(2020, Month.AUGUST, 29);
System.out.println(d2);

print ->
2020-10-01
2020-08-20
2020-08-29

